            <h5 class="project-titles">The<br class="show-for-lg"> animation</h5>
            <p>While creating this animation, I tried to capture the song’s bittersweet message through the clear and bright color palette with cinematographic lighting. I first came up with the script, compositions, and keyframes. I then created frame-by-frame illustrations in Photoshop and assembled the scenes together in After Effect.
            </p>
